ogdl

Class Graph

  • java.lang.Object
    • ogdl.Graph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<IGraph>, IGraph

    public class Graph
extends Object
implements IGraph
    This is a data structure for holding directed graphs, where all nodes are Strings, except leafs that can be any Object. The edges in the graph don't hold any information or attributes. $Id$ Initial date: 2001 oct 3 XXX Some functions not protected against cycles.
